snippet.title: WWE All Stars Greatest Trailer Featuring Rise Against
snippet.description: Featuring the new hit song by Rise Against, "Satellite", watch the greatest WWE All Star trailer featuring the greatest roster ever assembled in a WWE wrestling videogame. The brawler arcade madness that is WWE All Stars is now available in stores, so go get it brother!
